<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link70650" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=70650&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F172422-could-someone-use-little-words-and-explain%2Fanswers%2F70650-just-as-a-tree-can-be">flag</a>
</div>
